<div class="faq-section">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Frequently‑Asked Questions</h2>
    <p class="faq-content">
         What services does Players Club Management offer?<br />
                We provide NIL deal negotiation, brand partnership facilitation, marketing strategy development, financial literacy education, and
                personal brand coaching for student-athletes.<br><br>
                Who can sign with Players Club Management?<br />
                We work with high school and college athletes across various sports who are looking to maximize their NIL potential.<br><br>
                How does Players Club Management get paid?<br />
                We offer a tiered membership system, including a free entry-level tier. For higher-tier memberships, we require a $100 consulting fee
                deposit and take a 20% commission on any NIL deals secured.<br><br>
                How can brands collaborate with Players Club Management?<br />
                Brands looking to partner with our athletes can reach out through our "Connect With Us" button or email us directly. We will match
                brands with the right athletes based on target audience, values, and campaign goals.<br><br>
                Do you provide legal support for NIL contracts?<br />
                Yes, we work with legal professionals to ensure all NIL contracts are reviewed and compliant with NCAA and state regulations.<br><br>
                <a href="../Contact_Us/index.html"><span class="underline-text">Have more questions? Reach out to us today!</span></a>
    </p>
</div>
